701582f-a.title: Bronx: Paulding Avenue - Bogart Avenue
701582f-a.text:
Paulding Ave., west side, between its junction with Bogart and
Lydig Aves., showing the Morris Park station of the New York, Westchester
and Boston Railroad. The above location denotes the street on which
the depot faces.
About 1910.
